cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on generating high-resolution videos of human subjects using computer vision techniques. Specifically, it deals with human motion transfer and uses a GAN-based architecture to generate videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) as it generates videos. It uses deep learning techniques (cs.LG) and AI (cs.AI) to generate videos.
